file  pmlib_cpuidle.h
 This file declares the interface for CPU Idle functionality. This is is a low latency power saving mode which allows fast wakeup depending on the power mode set.
 
file  pmlib_cpuidle_pmmc.h
 This file declares the interface for PMMC CPU Idle functionality. This is a low latency power saving mode which allows fast wakeup depending on the power mode set.
 
file  pmlib_sysconfig.h
 This file declares the interface for the system configuration for switching on or switching off modules or putting them in HW controlled Auto Clock Gated mode.
 
file  pmlib_sysconfig_pmmc.h
 This file declares the interface for the system configuration for switching on or switching off modules or putting them in HW controlled Auto Clock Gated mode via the PMMC.
 
file  pmlib_videopll.h
 This file declares the interface for video pll programming.
